# Calculator

Welcome to the calculator project, part of my Codsoft internship tasks. This project is a simple web-based calculator that performs basic arithmetic operations.

## Table of Contents

- Introduction
- Features
- Technologies Used

## Introduction

This is a simple yet functional calculator that performs basic arithmetic operations. It is a great project for practicing HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Basic arithmetic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, division)
- Responsive design
- Clear button to reset the input

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
